title: Web5 Drinks with TBD & Race Capital
description: Product: tbDEX is an open source financial protocol that can move value anywhere around the world in a more cost-effective and efficient way than what’s possible today. Using tbDEX makes it easy to transfer money across borders — whether to relatives in other countries, employees in other jurisdictions, or suppliers around the world.
